Description: 
    Run user-defined command presets.

Usage: xl-cmd <Option>

Option: 

    -h , --help:
        Print this help page.

Configuration:
    Custom commands are added inside ~/.config/xlotus/cmd

    Syntax: <ICON>;<NAME>;<COMMAND>

    <COMMAND> can be preceded by:
          & => Run command asynchronously
        [i] => Run command interactively

    You don't need to provide full path of xlotus scripts.
